text: pachi sum te vyakti uttama che jene potani imaratano payo allahathi darava ane allahani prasannata mate rakhyo hoya athava te vyakti uttama che, jene potani imaratano payo ko'i khinana kinara para je padi javani hoya, rakhyo hoya? Pachi te tene la'ine jahannamani agamam padi jaya ane allaha ta'ala ava atyacari'one margadarsana nathi apato
